Class FieldFormat<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tibbo.aggregate.common.datatable.FieldFormat<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PublicCloneable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BooleanFieldFormat, ColorFieldFormat, DataFieldFormat, DataTableFieldFormat, DateFieldFormat, DoubleFieldFormat, FloatFieldFormat, IntFieldFormat, LongFieldFormat, StringFieldFormat

    public abstract class FieldFormat<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, PublicCloneable
    FieldFormat is a part of TableFormat that describes single DataTable field.
